Interface IDeviceRepositorySpringData

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<DeviceDataModel, String>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<DeviceDataModel, String>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<DeviceDataModel, String>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<DeviceDataModel, String>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<DeviceDataModel, String>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<DeviceDataModel>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<DeviceDataModel, String>
public interface IDeviceRepositorySpringData extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<DeviceDataModel,String>
Device Repository Spring Data This interface extends the JpaRepository interface from Spring Data JPA to provide database operations on Device entities. It provides methods to find devices by room identity, device type name, and device ID. It also provides a method to retrieve all device IDs in the repository.
